list.abstract: Bubble（英[ˈbʌbl]，美[ˈbʌbl]），英语单词。可做名词或动词用。做名词时，指泡、水泡、泡沫等；做动词时，指冒泡、起泡、沸腾等。英语短语有housing bubble（房地产泡沫），例句为Speed up their recovery from the housing bubble.（加快他们从房地产泡沫中复苏。） 复数为bubbles，第三人称单数为bubbles，现在分词为bubbling，过去式为bubbled，过去分词为bubbled。 近义词有foam（名词）、yeast（名词）、gush over（动词）等。
《泡泡》（バブル）是一部由志尊淳、りりあ、广濑爱丽丝等担任配音，荒木哲郎执导，虚渊玄、大樹連司、佐藤直子担任编剧的日本动画，于2022年5月13日在日本上映。 该动画讲述了世界各地降下一阵泡泡雨，东京与外界彻底隔绝，以危险的游戏风格闯出名号的年轻好手响，某天不慎失足，坠入扭转重力的海里，幸而被掌握神秘力量的女孩诗搭救，俩人竟听见别人完全无法耳闻的独特声响的故事。

yingyinNormal.en: The silverware gets bundled in rubber bands and then bubble wrapped. Got it? Yeah.
yingyinNormal.zh: 银器要先用橡胶膜捆上，然后用塑料泡沫包上。明白了没有？明白了。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah. My whole department's long on this stuff. They call me Chicken Little. They call me Bubble Boy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是的，我在的部门一直都是这样干的，他们叫我小鸡仔，叫我泡沫男孩。

yingyinNormal.en: And right suddenly we had Netscape, and we had Yahoo and we had, indeed, the entire dotcom bubble.
yingyinNormal.zh: 突然我们就有了Netscape，雅虎，然后是整个互联网的泡沫经济。

yingyinNormal.en: Daddy, Mummy. There's no more bubble mixture.
yingyinNormal.zh: 爸爸，妈妈！泡泡器吹不出泡泡啦！

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa, if you like bubbles, why don't you play with your bubble mixture? Yes. My bubble mixture.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩奇，既然你喜欢吹泡泡，不如你们来玩泡泡器？是的，玩我的泡泡器。

yingyinNormal.en: Now watch this. Daddy Pig has made his own bubble mixture.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在，仔细看好了。猪爸爸自己做了一个泡泡器。

yingyinNormal.en: I've got wine at my place and some bubble wrap we could pop.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我家有酒，我们还可以摁泡泡塑料包装。

yingyinNormal.en: I love bubbles. Oh, dear. The bubble mixture is all used up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我好喜欢泡泡！噢糟糕，泡泡器里面都空啦。

yingyinNormal.en: My passion bubble's very near the surface, I guess, not gonna lie.
yingyinNormal.zh: 大概是因为我的怒气细胞特别发达，我就是这么想的，没骗你。

yingyinNormal.en: George, wake up. Santa has been. Bubble makers, comics, and tangerines.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治，快点醒醒，圣诞老人来过了。吹泡泡器，和漫画还有一个橘子。

yingyinNormal.en: Don't take it off too soon. Let it bubble a bit, or you'll taste the flour.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别过早拿起来，让它沸腾一下，不然味道就不好了。

yingyinNormal.en: First, dip the stick in the mixture. Then, take a big breath and blow. Bubble.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第一步，先把棍子在里面沾一沾。接着，吸好大一口气，再吹出气。泡泡。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh dear. I've spilled all my bubble mixture. Now, we can't make any more bubbles.
yingyinNormal.zh: 噢糟糕，看来这个泡泡器也不能用了。所以我们现在吹不了泡泡了！

yingyinNormal.en: Six months ago, we took you to the dermatologist for taking too many bubble baths.
yingyinNormal.zh: 六个月前，你还因为泡了太多泡泡浴被我们带去看皮肤科医生。

yingyinNormal.en: When it gets there, the bubble surrounding the antibody fuses to the cell membrane.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当它到了那里，包着抗体的泡泡融入细胞膜。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you okay, Daddy Pig? Yes, I'm fine. Daddy Pig has made the biggest bubble ever.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你没事吧，猪爸爸？是的，我没事。猪爸爸打出了最大的泡泡。

yingyinNormal.en: That's a bit childish, isn't it? I'm sorry, and what flavor is your bubble gum cigar?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你这样有点幼稚了吧？真不好意思啊，你的泡泡糖雪茄啥口味来着？

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, well sorry to burst that bubble, Pheebs, but selfless good deeds don't exist. Okay?
yingyinNormal.zh: 菲比，很抱歉戳破你的美梦，世界上没有无私的善事。

yingyinNormal.en: So I'm gonna go and take a nice long hot bubble bath because you kids are driving me crazy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我现在要去洗个香喷喷热腾腾的泡泡浴，因为妈咪快要被你们逼疯了。

yingyinNormal.en: George, wake up. Santa has been. Bubble makers, comics, and tangerines. Mommy, Daddy, it's Christmas.
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔治，快点醒醒，圣诞老人来过了。吹泡泡器，和漫画还有一个橘子。爸爸妈妈，今天是圣诞节了。
